### ============================================================
### 04. 직급 관리
### ============================================================
### [사전 조건] admin 토큰 발급 (01-auth.http)
### ============================================================

### 직급 목록 조회 (member 이상이면 가능)
GET http://localhost:8081/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

###

### 직급 생성 (ADMIN 전용)
POST http://localhost:8081/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "사원",
  "level": 1
}

###

POST http://localhost:8081/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "대리",
  "level": 2
}

###

POST http://localhost:8081/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "과장",
  "level": 3
}
